OL,6,FFor hundreds affected by substance
OL,7,Fmisuse in the North West, recovery
OL,8,Fstarted with a walk.
OL,10,FA journey towards a life free from
OL,11,Fdependency began along a route around
OL,12,FDerry with ARC Fitness.
OL,14,FPeople can take part in the walk even
OL,15,Fif they are still in the grip of
OL,16,Faddiction.
