OL,6,FThose making their first tentative
OL,7,Fsteps are helped, supported,
OL,8,Fencouraged and inspired by walking
OL,9,Fcompanions who are further down their
OL,10,Froad to recovery.
OL,12,FThe walk is led every Monday and
OL,13,FFriday evening by Martin Ward.
OL,15,FHe's a recovering alcoholic and a
OL,16,Fcounsellor with Addiction Recovery
OL,17,FCoaching, known as ARC fitness.
OL,19,FMartin says many find it easier to
OL,20,Fopen up and talk while they walk:
