OL,6,F"It gives people a safe space, they
OL,7,Fcan talk about difficulties with
OL,8,Falcohol and drugs. Once they are
OL,9,Fwalking it's easier than a
OL,10,Fconversation in a room."
OL,12,FIt's just a year since Danielle
OL,13,FMcKinney first joined the walk.
OL,15,FShe was struggling with alcohol and
OL,16,Fpainkillers.
OL,18,FNow Danielle is clean and helping
OL,19,Fothers.
