OL,6,F"You know what it is like to start,'
OL,7,Fshe says: "You know how hard it is to
OL,8,Fgo on that first walk but for me I'm
OL,9,Fnow at that stage where I'm trying to
OL,10,Fhelp others so it worked really well
OL,11,Ffor me."
OL,13,FCollette McCallion lost everything
OL,14,Fwhen she was drinking, including her
OL,15,Ffamily.
OL,17,FJoining the walk helped her turn her
OL,18,Flife around: "I used to be embarrassed
OL,19,Fand ashamed," she told UTV: "I thought
OL,20,Fmy family was ashamed.
