OL,6,FNo shame is one of their mottos
OL,8,FGary believes the need for addiction
OL,9,Frecovery services is greater now than
OL,10,Fever
OL,12,F"The drug landscape is changing," he
OL,13,Fsays, "There is more and more
OL,14,Favailability and that is providing
OL,15,Fmore and more problems."
OL,17,FThe number of drug deaths in Northern
OL,18,FIreland has risen by 40% in 10 years.
