OL,6,FProfessor Anne Campbell is concerned
OL,7,Fthat many are young people aged 34 and
OL,8,Funder.
OL,10,FShe's part of the Northern Ireland
OL,11,FAlcohol and Drug Alliance and wants
OL,12,Fthe new Stormont Executive to
OL,13,Fprioritise tackling addiction.
OL,15,F"We do not want to be prophets of
OL,16,Fdoom," Prof Campbell warns, "But if we
OL,17,Fdo not put funding and the proper
OL,18,Fresources into this sector then
OL,19,Fproblems will only get worse."
